673 int open_gl(void) {
674 #ifndef IS_UWP
675  libGL = LoadLibraryW(L"opengl32.dll");
676  if (libGL != NULL) {
677  void (*tmp)(void);
678  tmp = (void (*)(void)) GetProcAddress(libGL, "wglGetProcAddress");
679  gladGetProcAddressPtr = (PFNWGLGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE) tmp;
680  return gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL;
681  }
682 #endif
683 
684  return 0;
685 }
686 
687 static
688 void close_gl(void) {
689  if (libGL != NULL) {
690  FreeLibrary((HMODULE) libGL);
691  libGL = NULL;
692  }
693 }
694 #else
695 #include <dlfcn.h>
696 static void* libGL;
697 
698 #if !defined(__APPLE__) && !defined(__HAIKU__)
699 typedef void* (APIENTRYP PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE) (const char* );
700 static PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE gladGetProcAddressPtr;
701 #endif
702 
703 static
704 int open_gl(void) {
705 #ifdef __APPLE__
706  static const char* NAMES[] = {
707  "../Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
708  "/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
709  "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
710  "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/Versions/Current/OpenGL"
711  };
712 #else
713  static const char* NAMES[] = { "libGL.so.1", "libGL.so" };
714 #endif
715 
716  unsigned int index = 0;
717  for (index = 0; index < (sizeof(NAMES) / sizeof(NAMES[0])); index++) {
718  libGL = dlopen(NAMES[index], RTLD_NOW | RTLD_GLOBAL);
719 
720  if (libGL != NULL) {
721 #if defined(__APPLE__) || defined(__HAIKU__)
722  return 1;
723 #else
724  gladGetProcAddressPtr = (PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE) dlsym(libGL,
725  "glXGetProcAddressARB");
726  return gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL;
727 #endif
728  }
729  }
730 
731  return 0;
732 }
733 
734 static
735 void close_gl(void) {
736  if (libGL != NULL) {
737  dlclose(libGL);
738  libGL = NULL;
739  }
740 }
741 #endif
742 
743 static
744 void* get_proc(const char* namez) {
745  void* result = NULL;
746  if (libGL == NULL)
747  return NULL;
748 
749 #if !defined(__APPLE__) && !defined(__HAIKU__)
750  if (gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL) {
751  result = gladGetProcAddressPtr(namez);
752  }
753 #endif
754  if (result == NULL) {
755 #if defined(_WIN32) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
756  result = (void *) GetProcAddress((HMODULE) libGL, namez);
757 #else
758  result = dlsym(libGL, namez);
759 #endif
760  }
761 
762  return result;
763 }
764 
765 int gladLoadGL(void) {
766  int status = 0;
767 
768  if (open_gl()) {
769  status = gladLoadGLLoader(&get_proc);
770  close_gl();
771  }
772 
773  return status;
774 }
775 
776 struct gladGLversionStruct GLVersion = { 0, 0 };
777 
778 #if defined(GL_ES_VERSION_3_0) || defined(GL_VERSION_3_0)
779 #define _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION 1
780 #endif
781 
782 static int max_loaded_major;
783 static int max_loaded_minor;
784 
785 static const char* exts = NULL;
786 static int num_exts_i = 0;
787 static char** exts_i = NULL;
788 
789 static int get_exts(void) {
790 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
791  if (max_loaded_major < 3) {
792 #endif
793  exts = (const char *) glGetString(GL_EXTENSIONS);
794 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
795  } else {
796  unsigned int index;
797 
798  num_exts_i = 0;
799  glGetIntegerv(GL_NUM_EXTENSIONS, &num_exts_i);
800  if (num_exts_i > 0) {
801  exts_i = (char **) malloc((size_t) num_exts_i * (sizeof *exts_i));
802  }
803 
804  if (exts_i == NULL) {
805  return 0;
806  }
807 
808  for (index = 0; index < (unsigned) num_exts_i; index++) {
809  const char* gl_str_tmp =
810  (const char *) glGetStringi(GL_EXTENSIONS, index);
811  size_t len = strlen(gl_str_tmp);
812 
813  char* local_str = (char *) malloc((len + 1) * sizeof(char));
814  if (local_str != NULL) {
815  memcpy(local_str, gl_str_tmp, (len + 1) * sizeof(char));
816  }
817  exts_i[index] = local_str;
818  }
819  }
820 #endif
821  return 1;
822 }
823 
824 static void free_exts(void) {
825  if (exts_i != NULL) {
826  int index;
827  for (index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
828  free((char *) exts_i[index]);
829  }
830  free((void *) exts_i);
831  exts_i = NULL;
832  }
833 }
834 
835 static int has_ext(const char* ext) {
836 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
837  if (max_loaded_major < 3) {
838 #endif
839  const char* extensions;
840  const char* loc;
841  const char* terminator;
842  extensions = exts;
843  if (extensions == NULL || ext == NULL) {
844  return 0;
845  }
846 
847  while (1) {
848  loc = strstr(extensions, ext);
849  if (loc == NULL) {
850  return 0;
851  }
852 
853  terminator = loc + strlen(ext);
854  if ((loc == extensions || *(loc - 1) == ' ') &&
855  (*terminator == ' ' || *terminator == '\0')) {
856  return 1;
857  }
858  extensions = terminator;
859  }
860 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
861  } else {
862  int index;
863  if (exts_i == NULL)
864  return 0;
865  for (index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
866  const char* e = exts_i[index];
867 
868  if (exts_i[index] != NULL && strcmp(e, ext) == 0) {
869  return 1;
870  }
871  }
872  }
873 #endif
874 
875  return 0;
876 }

12072 
12073 static void find_coreGL(void) {
12074 
12075  /* Thank you @elmindreda
12076  * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
12077  * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
12078  */
12079  int i, major, minor;
12080 
12081  const char* version;
12082  const char* prefixes[] = {
12083  "OpenGL ES-CM ",
12084  "OpenGL ES-CL ",
12085  "OpenGL ES ",
12086  NULL
12087  };
12088 
12089  version = (const char *) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
12090  if (!version)
12091  return;
12092 
12093  for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
12094  const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
12095  if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
12096  version += length;
12097  break;
12098  }
12099  }
12100 
12101 /* PR #18 */
12102 #ifdef _MSC_VER
12103  sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
12104 #else
12105  sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
12106 #endif
12107 
12108  GLVersion.major = major;
12109  GLVersion.minor = minor;
12110  max_loaded_major = major;
12111  max_loaded_minor = minor;
12112  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_0 = (major == 1 && minor >= 0) || major > 1;
12113  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_1 = (major == 1 && minor >= 1) || major > 1;
12114  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_2 = (major == 1 && minor >= 2) || major > 1;
12115  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_3 = (major == 1 && minor >= 3) || major > 1;
12116  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_4 = (major == 1 && minor >= 4) || major > 1;
12117  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_5 = (major == 1 && minor >= 5) || major > 1;
12118  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_0 = (major == 2 && minor >= 0) || major > 2;
12119  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_1 = (major == 2 && minor >= 1) || major > 2;
12120  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_0 = (major == 3 && minor >= 0) || major > 3;
12121  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_1 = (major == 3 && minor >= 1) || major > 3;
12122  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_2 = (major == 3 && minor >= 2) || major > 3;
12123  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_3 = (major == 3 && minor >= 3) || major > 3;
12124  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_0 = (major == 4 && minor >= 0) || major > 4;
12125  if (GLVersion.major > 4 || (GLVersion.major >= 4 && GLVersion.minor >= 0)) {
12126  max_loaded_major = 4;
12127  max_loaded_minor = 0;
12128  }
12129 }
12130 
12131 int gladLoadGLLoader(GLADloadproc load) {
12132  GLVersion.major = 0;
12133  GLVersion.minor = 0;
12134  glGetString = (PFNGLGETSTRINGPROC) load("glGetString");
12135  if (glGetString == NULL)
12136  return 0;
12137  if (glGetString(GL_VERSION) == NULL)
12138  return 0;
12139  find_coreGL();
12140  load_GL_VERSION_1_0(load);
12141  load_GL_VERSION_1_1(load);
12142  load_GL_VERSION_1_2(load);

12145  load_GL_VERSION_1_5(load);

12155  return 0;
